            <summary>The volume contains 97 leaves. Folios 1a, 17a, 18b, and an
                            unnumbered folio between 17 and 18 are blank. There are four preliminary
                            folios: folio ia has Arabic and Latin titles for the first item in the
                            volume, with the lower quarter torn away; folios iia, iiia, and ivab
                            have Arabic pious phrases, prayers, and a note of purchase for 20
                            dinars, written in Maghrib&#x12B; script; folios ib, iib, and iiib are
                            blank.</summary>
